OL,3,CJail for ringleader of staged doorstep
OL,4,Cgun threat plot
OL,6,FThe boyfriend of a woman who was
OL,7,Finvolved in a bitter divorce dispute
OL,8,Fhas been jailed for plotting to frame
OL,9,Fher estranged husband in a bizarre
OL,10,Fstaged gun threat.
OL,12,FSabu Singh's girlfriend Hardeep Sangha
OL,13,Fwas at home in Shadwell, Leeds, when
OL,14,Ftwo masked men turned up on her
OL,15,Fdoorstep apparently to threaten her
OL,16,Fbrother, Inderjeet Gosal.
