OL,3,CJail for ringleader of staged doorstep
OL,4,Cgun threat plot
OL,6,FCCTV captured the moment they
OL,7,Fbrandished what appeared to be a long-
OL,8,Fbarrelled firearm and told Gosal:
OL,9,F"Stay out of Jonny's business, stay
OL,10,Fout of your sister's case."
OL,12,F"Jonny" was Hardeep's estranged
OL,13,Fhusband Harpal Sangha.
OL,15,FMr Sangha was arrested on suspicion of
OL,16,Fwitness intimidation on 1 August 2020,
OL,17,Fthe day after the apparent gun threat.
OL,19,FHowever, telltale laughter on the CCTV
OL,20,Ffootage triggered police suspicions
OL,21,Fabout his involvement in the incident.
