OL,3,CJail for ringleader of staged doorstep
OL,4,Cgun threat plot
OL,6,FDetectives identified the gunmen as 16-
OL,7,Fyear-old Kane Allen and Matias Jozio,
OL,8,Faged 17.
OL,10,FTelephone evidence showed Allen in
OL,11,Fcontact with Sabu Singh on the day of
OL,12,Fthe incident and Singh in contact with
OL,13,FHardeep Sangha and the Gosals.
OL,15,FSingh was shown to be the main
OL,16,Forchestrator of the plot to
OL,17,Fincriminate Harpal Sangha, police said.
