OL,3,CJail for ringleader of staged doorstep
OL,4,Cgun threat plot
OL,6,FHe was arrested in September 2020,
OL,7,Falong with Hardeep Sangha, Inderjeet
OL,8,FGosal and Gosal's wife, Harpreet, who
OL,9,Fhad also been involved in the plot.
OL,11,FAn audio recording recovered from
OL,12,FInderjeet Gosal's phone showed those
OL,13,Finvolved in the plot meeting in
OL,14,FOakwood to discuss their plans.
OL,16,FSingh gave no comment during his
OL,17,Finterviews after initially denying any
OL,18,Fknowledge of the gun threat incident.
OL,1,Woz5~k4{$z%~s1z5jw=hw1         G4/7
