OL,3,CJail for ringleader of staged doorstep
OL,4,Cgun threat plot
OL,6,FBut all six of those involved were
OL,7,Fcharged with conspiracy to pervert the
OL,8,Fcourse of justice. Singh, Allen and
OL,9,FJozio also charged with conspiracy to
OL,10,Fcommit criminal damage in relation to
OL,11,Fan attack on a shop.
OL,13,FAll but Singh were sentenced at Leeds
OL,14,FCrown Court in August this year.
OL,16,FThe 49-year-old, of Sandhill Lane,
OL,17,FMoortown, has now been jailed for
OL,18,Fthree years and seven months.
