OL,3,CJail for ringleader of staged doorstep
OL,4,Cgun threat plot
OL,6,FDet Ch insp Michael Herbert, of Leeds
OL,7,FDistrict CID, said: "The criminal use
OL,8,Fof firearms is something the police
OL,9,Fwill always treat extremely seriously,
OL,10,Fand a report of a man being threatened
OL,11,Fat gunpoint on the doorstep of his
OL,12,Ffamily home was a real cause for
OL,13,Fconcern that attracted a significant
OL,14,Fpolice response and investigation.
OL,16,F"Those involved clearly underestimated
OL,17,Fthe level of focus that we apply to a
OL,18,Fserious incident such as this.
